# SHA-256 checksums for packaged migrations.
#
# Format: <id>  <sha256>  <filename>
# - <id>       4-digit zero-padded integer matching the filename prefix
# - <sha256>   64-char lowercase hex
# - <filename> basename of the migration file
#
# Regenerate via: python -m orchestrator.db.migrate_tools regenerate-checksums
# Pinning the checksum manifest defends against supply-chain tamper of migration
# files — an attacker cannot alter a migration and its manifest row in the same
# commit without detection in code review.
